      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey can u help me write a rejection email? for a candidate who made it to the final round for a software engineer role but we decided to go with someone else. needs to sound professional but not like a robot, kinda empathetic so they dont feel bad since they did well in the interviews.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
